Relax on the private back patio—oh, and 2 outside storage sheds. Did I mention the location? Located in the desirable KNOLL RUN section of Gloucester Twp. EZ access to 42, shopping and eateries. LOW TAXES TOO! ***Assocation is $210.00 monthly
